1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:09,815
From its humble beginnings in the early 20th century, IIT (ISM) Dhanbad has forged an
extraordinary legacy, transforming vision into impactful reality.

2
00:00:09,915 --> 00:00:17,956
Established in 1926, this esteemed institution has stood tall for nearly a century,
steadily evolving through the millennium.

3
00:00:18,056 --> 00:00:33,649
What began as the Indian School of Mines has blossomed into a full-fledged Indian
Institute of Technology, operating with 18 vibrant branches across Engineering, Applied
Sciences, Management Studies, and Humanities, cementing its place as a prominent global
institution.

4
00:00:33,749 --> 00:00:40,910
This transformation marks a new era, building upon a centenary of outperforming
achievements in both academia and industry.

5
00:00:41,010 --> 00:00:48,903
Our campus is a hub of comprehensive learning, offering a diverse array of undergraduate,
postgraduate, and PhD programs.

6
00:00:49,003 --> 00:00:54,318
We foster a rich environment for research, leading to groundbreaking contributions.

7
00:00:54,418 --> 00:01:05,041
From pioneering the nation's first Geoarchaeology course to a unique integrated BTech-MBA
program with IIM Mumbai, our academic offerings reflect a commitment to forward-thinking
education.

8
00:01:05,141 --> 00:01:17,881
Faculty members are not just educators but innovators, with individuals like Prof Sekhar
Dutta becoming Fellows of the Institution of Civil Engineers, UK, and Prof Anshumali
shaping climate change policy.

9
00:01:17,981 --> 00:01:26,413
Our researchers, like the team that conducted the first-ever multiple-layered blasting
using smart design, are at the forefront of industrial innovation.

10
00:01:26,513 --> 00:01:39,401
IIT (ISM) Dhanbad shines on the global stage, proudly securing the 20th position worldwide
in Engineering-Mineral and Mining in QS rankings, a significant leap and a testament to
our specialized excellence.

11
00:01:39,501 --> 00:01:49,915
Our reach extends beyond the campus gates through vital community work, including skill
development programs for local youth and leadership training for Panchayati Raj
Functionaries.

12
00:01:50,015 --> 00:02:03,667
We embrace inclusivity, as demonstrated by the Uttar Pradesh government's support for Atul
Kumar's IIT education following Supreme Court intervention, and our commitment to student
well-being through initiatives like a fully operational campus creche.

13
00:02:03,767 --> 00:02:12,188
Our alumni, such as Ms Gargi Mishra, recognized among the top 100 inspiring women in
mining globally, continue to make us proud.

14
00:02:12,288 --> 00:02:18,901
Even moments of campus joy, like the viral Diwali rocket video, add to the vibrant
tapestry of student life.

15
00:02:19,001 --> 00:02:32,352
As we continue to drive India's critical mineral mission and innovate in fields from
Arctic MedTech to Hydrogen Valley development, IIT (ISM) Dhanbad remains dedicated to
shaping future leaders and contributing to a brighter tomorrow.

